channel.title: Who are you? Swedish guy with mopar sweater and norrlandsguld ;D
channel.description:
This isn't an ordinary question but... I'm looking for a member here.
Today in Sweden I saw a person with the mopar symbol on the back of a black sweater.
Swedish: Vem fan var du i Västerås som cyklade förbi coop extra idag med en svart mopar tröjja och en låda norrlands under armen? ;) :D

item.title: Who are you? Swedish guy with mopar sweater and norrlandsguld ;D
item.dc:creator: @CheeterFromSythe CheeterFromSythe
item.description:
@CheeterFromSythe wrote:

[quote=“BloodRayne, post:3, topic:237098”]Nicely put, R.I.P.

Is that the symbol you saw? If so, then yeah, just a car person. Mitb doesn’t sell shirts anyways, unless it was custom made c;[/quote]
Yeah that was the logo.
Damn I thought that Mopar (The RS cheating one) had custom made that M for himself

And I know Speljohan and he lives in southern Sweden in a city called Laholm
And I don’t think he would wear a moparisthebest sweater either xD
